Package common.test

Data structures for holding test information
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LongAnswerQuestion
    Represents a question which is responded to with a long form answer and graded manually
    MultipartQuestion
    Represents a question made up of multiple sub-questions
    MultipleChoiceAnswer
    Represents an answer to a MultipleChoiceQuestion
    MultipleChoiceQuestion
    Represents a question for which the user can select one (or more) answers from a list
    NetMultipleChoiceQuestion
    Represents a MultipleChoiceQuestion which is stripped of all correct answer information
    NetQuestion
    Represents a Question which does not contain any correct answer information
    NetShortAnswerQuestion
    Represents a ShortAnswerQuestion which is stripped of all correct answer information
    NetTest
    Represents a Test which does not contain any correct answer information
    Question
    Represents a question which will appear on a test
    ShortAnswerQuestion
    Represents a question which is intended to have a short answer and is optionally graded automatically
    Test
    Represents a test and all its associated data
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Language
    Specifies the programming language for which tests are written
    QuestionType
    Represents the type of a question
    TestDifficulty
    Represents the difficulty of a test
